Class Email

  • java.lang.Object
    • DataStructures.Email

  • public class Email
extends java.lang.Object
    This Email class is the basic messaging class that goes between accounts. Contains lists of users it is to be sent to, who it's from, and the message it contains Identified by a unique ID
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Clark Chambers
